Author: Exile13#4458
Content:
`1.  ./komodo-cli getnewaddress  (this gets a new address)
2.  ./komodo-cli dumprivkey <ADDRESS FROM ABOVE>  (this gets the wif)
3.  ./komodo-cli validataddress <ADRESS FROM STEP 1> (this gets pubkey)`
